Joanna Kerns https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanna_Kerns 0 Joanna Kerns (born February 12, 1953) is an American actress and director best known for her role as Maggie Seaver on the family situation comedy Growing Pains from 1985 to 1992.
